{"tid":1380484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對付速龍","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:31:16.000Z","uid":265339,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d97486a4397ffec71ddcca1121082934d8851549","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"P牌慎屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n速龍小隊基本上都係十幾個沖埋黎捉人，佢地一沖大家都怯，一怯就散，一散就有人落單，一落單就有人俾人拉。我建議佢地沖向中間既義士既時候，左右兩邊既人應該向左右兩邊退唔好向後退，中間首當其沖既就應該向後退，咁就會變成左右兩邊既人夾住左中間班速龍，呢個時候一定要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還拖，還拖，還拖，搶GEAR，搶GEAR，搶GEAR</span></span></strong></span>，還完拖或者搶到GEAR就要一齊退後，要避免班防暴沖上黎救速龍，所以要做得好快同好有默契。以上建議實行起上黎難度真係好高，一黎無受過訓練，二黎無人指揮，三黎真係怯，所以最好真係避免落入要留守既情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRXhwnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRXhwnr.png&h=b892ede0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df42451003fb5ea113260beacda5275117be9e0e","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd701acdd126aedf42a05cc57e4e738010443086","tid":1380484,"uid":230036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"最重要唔好一俾狗衝就退 仲有d點都堅守既前線就會即刻俾狗圍"},{"pid":"32459397b1af8a1f67ebda11978581a09daef10a","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"有tg都唔好後退，後退食得仲多煙，要向前行"},{"pid":"7d07e6cd62320c8205299b23a230162af604a06a","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97abe0f3475fb8dc098ed2e6a6ceba8403b22b18","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3cbbc75c5af3814696240e01ba30ef2c7ce486f","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff39f7e4ba3c8b47891cb1577b103c880e15a5cc","tid":1380484,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n西環亂港 還我自由！<br />\n警黑勾結 不公不義！<br />\n寧為玉碎 不作瓦全！<br />\n<br />\n［重開］全 港 性 大 罷 工 ！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380497\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380497</a></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"398e8a47dedf368a48913a9140fdfe67c9c7583a","tid":1380484,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"打佢地老味！打到佢地唔敢衝"},{"pid":"00970ee3f33f9b5ecc166a7ae8531648205d552c","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6501844706a01e1cb9c67c1c88b9797f10012bf1","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"要突破心理關口，突破唔到要盡快撤離"},{"pid":"6cf2098caf55759f4383076f67b043243630d3b0","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6adf2a26f79b0526ceb422e5071bc245ca0da47","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"252b85f9846d00ef22872e54fb939553f27def35","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6741e0d88d40e0304df0aa7b1ca689366039652","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39f17bc1640b8ac9166ce16f4ff654757f32b311","tid":1380484,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61994b7cc0d73140a3